    "claim_boundary": "Strict neutral dimension diagnostic for the record-feature quotient after H3 fitted points, cap normals, S2 axes, screen coordinates, radial depth, and modular depth have been excluded. It is not a measurement of the support-visible S2/H3 chart dimension, which is the separate D3 Lorentz/H3 chart branch. The finite-regulator gate uses the median of correlation and local-MLE estimators plus a pairwise-gap bound, because planted 3D controls show a small finite-sample low bias in the correlation estimator. The spectral proxy is reported but not gated because it is not calibrated on the finite planted controls. This is not sufficient for strict neutral bulk without leakage, controls, and refinement gates."
  },
